* Curley braces are prefixed with a newline:
if (...)
{
    // Stuff
}
* Indenting happens with 4 spaces (no tabs) each level
* Namespaces should stick (ie. no 'using namespace X').
* Hungarian notation: Not anymore
* STL is nice; use it :-)
* If possible/reasonable keep #include's out of headers (use class and such)
* All source files start with Copyright notice
